channel.title: Ive Been Away Alooong Time!
channel.description:
Ok well I just thought I might state that I have returned after an unexpected leave from Mopar :(
Family issues led me to leave for approximately 10 months in which time Jagex Nerfed Runescape and Mopar has evolved into a community full of leechers and new Users.
Not to mention the new Clients we have now...
I read up on my Java Docs again and found out something interesting :O Learn something new Everyday!
So I started to build up my client and was wondering if anyone wanted to help :O?
Anyways I didnt know where to place so I placed it here as Im going for Private Server Clients :D
So yeah, Im BACK!
